    "body": "I am seeing the same issue specifically when using a worktree of a bare repository. The following reproduces when using the default configuration (no starship.toml configuration is present):\n```\ngit clone --bare https://github.com/starship/starship starship-bare-repo\ncd starship-bare-repo\ngit worktree add -b my-bare-repo-worktree ../my-bare-repo-worktree\ncd ../my-bare-repo-worktree\nrm -f README.md\n```\n\nThe expected behaviour is to see and indicator that a file was deleted (default is [x] in red), instead no indicator is shown when using Starship 1.25.0. When using 1.24.2 the indicator is shown as expected.",
