    "updated_at": "2026-04-24T00:50:49Z",
    "body": "The useful evidence from our repo (courtesy of Codex gpt-5.5):\n\n```\ngit rev-parse --is-bare-repository      # false\ngit rev-parse --is-inside-work-tree     # true\nstarship trace: This is a bare repository, git_status is not applicable\n```\n\nSo, Starship’s check is too blunt: it is treating the bare common repo behind the linked\nworktree as if the current checkout itself were bare.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
